Changelog of E16DST
[2024-03-22]
	- DST0
		- add trigger hit and scaler of the new scintillator

[2024-03-21]
	- DST0
		- E16DST_GammaVetoScintillatorHit etc... are added
		- Version 5 -> 6

[2021-06-21]
	- DST0
		- dst0 for run0c trigger data
		- Version 4 -> 5

[2020-12-25]
	- DST0
	  - dst0 for run0b trigger data
		- Version 3 -> 4

[2020-12-04]
	- DST0
		- fix number of max track from 16 to 128

[2020-09-14]
	- DST0
		- fix number of max track from 8 to 16

[2020-08-12]
	- DST0
		- add time stamp in spill to EventHeader
		- Version 2 -> 3

[2020-08-06]
	- make this independent repository

[2020-07-21]
	- DST0
		- add auto mode to compress type
			- compress mode will be decided by file extensions

[2020-07-15]
	- DST0
		- add triggerAccept, physicsTriggerAccept, and physicsTriggerRequest to E16DST_DST0UT3
		- add DST0UT3 to ScalerEvent

[2020-07-11]
	- DST0
		- add number of events in spill and shot number to SpillStartEvent
		- update Version 1 -> 2

[2020-07-10]
	- DST0
		- modify EventHeader check logic
			- this is impremented in "E16DST_DST0EventHeader::Append"
			- only EventID, TimeStamp, SpillID will be checked

[2020-07-07]
	- DST0
		- add E16DST_File class, this is abstract class for file interface
		- add gzip mode (E16DST_GZFile)
		- change default value of compression type (NonCompressed -> ZlibGzip)

[2020-06-30]
	- DST0
		- add MRPC hits (and DetectorHeader of MRPC) to PhysicsEvent
		- add ESC hits (and DetectorHeader of ESC) to PhysicsEvent
		- add TSC hits (and DetectorHeader of TSC) to PhysicsEvent
		- update Version 0 -> Version 1
		- remove codes (already commented out from before) related to HitV

[2020-05-30]
	- DST0
		- add EventHeader check to EventHeader::Append
		- add discard flag to EventBuilder

[2020-05-25]
	- DST0
		- add TriggerData to EventHeader
		- bug fix for E16DST_DST0EventBuilder
			- EventHeader was reset when previous version of dst0_merger was used

[2020-05-21]
	- DST0
		- add TDC (uint32_t) to SSDHit

[2020-05-20]
	- DST0
		- change the type of UT3Track::time (uint32_t -> int64_t)

[2020-05-19]
	- DST0
		- remove busyTime from E16DST_DSt0Scaler
		- add busyTimeMerger[NMerger] to E16DST_DST0UT3
		- add SpillStartEvent and SpillEndEvent, NEventTypes is 4
		- uint32_t UT3::triggerType -> uint16_t UT3::triggerFlag + uint16_t UT3::triggerType
		- rename runID to runNumber
		- rename table directory from "table" to "channel_map"

[2020-05-15]
	- DST0
		- remove timestamp from LGHit
		- add timestamp (64 bits) to EventHeader

[2020-05-11]
